OL,6,FThe review states: "We support the
OL,7,Femployment and engagement of local
OL,8,FJersey residents over the use of
OL,9,Fconsultants wherever practical, as it
OL,10,Freduces the need for more expensive
OL,11,Fconsultancy or agency staff while
OL,12,Fproviding excellent employment
OL,13,Fopportunities locally.
OL,15,F"This should also be supplemented by
OL,16,Fmore provision of internal training to
OL,17,Fhelp upskill staff in these areas.
