OL,6,F"Health Services have made some
OL,7,Fprogress, but more effort is needed to
OL,8,Festablish a paid training program for
OL,9,Flocal residents to fill vacancies in
OL,10,Fthe medium term."
OL,12,FThe Public Accounts review was
OL,13,Fpublished along with a list of 10
OL,14,Frecommendations:
