OL,6,F"Health's IT projects need rigorous
OL,7,Fmonitoring to ensure patient outcomes
OL,8,Fand cost efficiency, while recruitment
OL,9,Fchallenges in Health require proactive
OL,10,Fsolutions to reduce waiting times and
OL,11,Fmanage rising costs.
OL,13,F"Additionally, we must address overall
OL,14,Fgovernment cost increases, enhance the
OL,15,Fclarity and accessibility of annual
OL,16,Freports, and improve local training
OL,17,Fprograms to reduce reliance on costly
OL,18,Fconsultants.
